D.q[6148] = "So what about those souls I asked you for?";
D.q[5324] = "I have other business to do, but I\'ll see you very soon.";
D.q[4337] = "Xephires will await you in the Tower of Bonta - remember, that\'s where you found the piece of that letter the first time. Be careful not to get caught with the jewel.";
D.q[6144] = "So what about those souls I asked you for?";
D.q[6528] = "Listen to me before you do anything stupid, I\'ve won a lot of money recently and I\'m in a position to pay Oto Mustam back with interest. I know I should have paid him back two weeks ago but I didn\'t have the means to do so. You\'re not going to kill me when I\'ve what your boss wants, are you? Listen, I\'d love to, I mean, I could satisfy your every desire if you let me live. What do you think?";
D.q[7401] = "";
D.q[5325] = "";
D.q[987] = "Did you find what I asked you fow?";
D.q[6897] = "Is that a real Hypnomeow? Unbelievable! It\'s been years since I\'ve seen one, well, not a live one, anyway.\nSo you\'d like me to train it to take part in interrogations? It\'d be a pleasure, it\'ll be a nice change from training Whitish Fangs.\nTell Ture Inge I\'ll let him know as soon as the Hypnomeow is ready.";
D.q[2239] = "Did y... did you find my... teddy...?";
D.q[6069] = "";
D.q[2340] = "Did you find the beast that is terrorising my animals? Please come see me when you\'re sure it has been... taken care of.";
D.q[7447] = "";
D.q[4170] = "Did you find the items I need?";
D.q[5821] = "";
D.q[2818] = "Listen to me, little new comer, I should be teaching you the three basic commandments: Drink, Guzzle, Fight, but I don\'t have time to do so... Hurry and go see Gasdaure: say hello for me and tell him I\'m sending you.\nLeave the island and go to Astrub, Eastwards. Gasdaure lives there... Don\'t come back until you\'re an experienced warrior. Don\'t forget to try all the local drinks, you\'ll appreciate ours all the more when you come back.";
D.q[6259] = "Listen, I\'m not the type to get mixed up in other peoples\' business, so let me tell you this. I\'ll pass on your message, and then, finito, that\'s it. And you know where you can stick your threats. It\'s not today nor tomorrow that a Sacrier is going to tremble before you.";
D.q[6362] = "Did you know... there are more than three thousand varieties of potato in the World of Twelve. Most are inedible, but that still leaves plenty of types to spice up your meals. Did you know there\'s a difference between the Phatato and the Pratato for example? The first is used for basic soldier\'s food while the second is usually eaten at breakfast on top of warm toast.";
D.q[1465] = "Dik yik kniwik tkik ikfik ink itik is is big is ink tirtinnik-stirik bildiknik, its cirik wild bik is big is ink silik grinik inik inik tik sivint flir inik tik ilictrik ifik tik firksitik lik wild riminik invisiblik ti tik nikid ik inik wild bik inik tik firksitik inik liksitik stirik?";
D.q[481] = "At the moment, I\'m way too busy looking for Halouine\'s treasure. I heard that every year at this period, a secret passage to the treasure opens up. I\'m interested because people say it contains a book which explains how to create a very powerful Pumpkwin mask.";
D.q[2048] = "Al right! Cunning is the one who wins a bet with a Xelor, right! They\'re said to read the future, but I believe that she\'s in love, that\'s all she can think about, so...the future...right!";
D.q[2787] = "Listen, they changed guards since I arrived. The new ones don\'t know my problem and they made the mistake of sticking you in with me... Let me explain. You can\'t get through those bars. But I can when I take this form... unfortunately, I\'m as blind as a drunken Enutrof. You\'re going to guide me around the room for me to find the key and bring it back to you. The guard near the exit has the key.";
D.q[7402] = "";
D.q[1468] = "Dik yik kniwik tkik ikfik yik wik ti kniwik itik which distincik tik lightniknik strick, yik jiksitik nid ti cinik tik nimbik ifik sicinds tirik irik bitwinik tik tindirbiltik inik tik lightniknik? Ich sicinik riprisints ibik trik picik.";
D.q[1733] = "Disciple, you still have many things to learn, what do you want to know ?";
D.q[1740] = "Disciple, you still have many things to learn, what do you want to know ?";
